Arduino-Watcher


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPLOYMENT

* Rename logging.conf_example and watcher.yml_example to logging.conf resp. watcher.yml and edit according to your needs.

* Copy cgi-bin/load on your webserver and assign the path to 'load_url'
in watcher.yml 

* Set up the Arduino board as detailed in circuit_diagram.png and load the
sketch /arduino/setled.ino

* Start the daemon in bin/

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Arduino::Watcher


